sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant Watcher as Git Watcher
participant Router as GraphMessageRouter
participant App as Look Graph Webview
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as GetGraphDataUseCase
participant Repo as GitRepository implements GitHistoryOperations
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

Watcher-->>Router: repositoryChanged(repositoryLocator)
Router-->>App: graph/refreshRequested
App->>Router: graph/dataRequest(repositoryLocator, CurrentCursorPageRequest, filters, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Repo
Router->>UseCase: execute(Repo, filters, CurrentCursorPageRequest, signal)
UseCase->>Repo: getCommitGraph(filters, CurrentCursorPageRequest, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, CurrentCursorPageRequest, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, CurrentCursorPageRequest, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: Page(GitCommit)
Runtime-->>Repo: Page(GitCommit)
Repo-->>UseCase: Page(GitCommit)
UseCase-->>Router: GraphData
Router-->>App: graph/dataResponse(requestId, GraphData)
App->>App: compare GraphData with current state
alt data changed
  App->>App: reduce with new graph state
else data unchanged
  App->>App: clear refreshing without replacing rows
end
